# Password Strength Analyzer & Data Breach Checker #

This project evaluates the strength of a given password and checks whether it has been involved in any known data breaches using a custom API.

## Features
- Password strength analysis based on common security criteria.
- Data breach checks via an API.

## How to Use
1. Clone this repository: `git clone https://github.com/your-username/password-checker.git`
2. Install dependencies: `pip install requests`
3. Run the script: `python password_checker.py`

## API Details
- Endpoint: `https://your-api.com/check-password`
- Method: `POST`
- Payload: `{ "password": "your-password" }`
- Response:
  ```json
  {
    "breached": true,
    "count": 12345
  }
